(* Proof:
   By Group_def and EXTENSION this is to show:
   (1) G* = G /\ x IN G ==> ?y. y IN G /\ (y * x = #e)
       Note x IN G ==> x IN G*          by G* = G
        ==> ?y. y IN G /\ (y * x = #e)  by monoid_invertibles_element
